// Template for `Local.xcconfig` — copy this file to `Local.xcconfig`
// (same directory) and fill in your own values. The real file is
// gitignored so each contributor keeps their own copy without it
// ever ending up in commits.
//
// PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER
//   Free Apple accounts can't share a bundle ID across personal
//   teams. Pick something unique to you, e.g. `YourName.Addit` or
//   `com.yourname.addit`. Apple will refuse signing if someone
//   else's free team has already claimed the same string.
//
// DEVELOPMENT_TEAM
//   The 10-character team ID for your Apple ID. Find it in:
//     Xcode → Settings → Accounts → click your Apple ID
//     → "Personal Team" row → copy the code in the "Team ID" column.

PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER = YourName.Addit
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = ABCDE12345
